40|$|The {{object of}} investigation: he-rats of the Vistar line. The work {{is aimed at}} studing {{the role of the}} 1, 4 -dihydropiridine-sensitive calcium {{channels}} in the development and suppression of the axute epileptic activity and the durable process of the chronic epileptization of the brain. It has been established, that niphedipine, <b>riodipine,</b> IOS- 1. 1212, PN 200 - 110 render the expresses antiepileptic action on the focal, acute generalized epileptic activity and the formation of the high convulse readiness of the brain. They are not effective against the convulsions after the process of the brain epileptization is completed. The obtained results are the justification for the expediency of including the blockers of the potential-sensitive calcium channels of group 1, 4 -dihydropiridines into the complex pathogenetic epilepsy therapy to be developedAvailable from VNTIC / VNTIC - Scientific & Technical Information Centre of RussiaSIGLERURussian Federatio...|$|E

